{"id": "1454466729714389033", "channel_id": "1454438358351609857", "type": 0, "author_id": "490103516078276630", "author_name": "noeyebunny.nobunsu", "author_bot": false, "content": "It's still working in process and I might not take it too seriously.\nBut still I write it anyway.\n[Mature contains warning]\n\nNoah was one of Sculpture Association's victim who died from the experiment of Dissolution.\nBefore she died, she met N who gives her another chance to live, but her life was too terrible to bear, she rejects it.\nHowever, N still gave it anyway because he wants to see what she gonna do with that.\nLater, she found by Mythag and taken to there.\nNow she wants to meet N again after she finds out that it's not bad to be alive.\nSurely she is his biggest fan.\n\nI think she is Caro realm because after she became Awakener, she always seek the way to die and failed\nso now she starts to do self harm instead and she might join Leigh for that too.", "timestamp": "2025-12-27T13:31:31.049000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Calm", "emoji_id": "1400771586545553408", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
